for dinner next time. I'll cook.

711
00:41:47,260 --> 00:41:49,672
Speaking of the kids' marriage,

712
00:41:49,672 --> 00:41:52,480
meeting the in-laws is all about fate, right?

713
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:54,320
- Yeah...
- Dad.

714
00:41:54,320 --> 00:41:57,931
Let's not talk about the in-laws. No.

715
00:41:57,931 --> 00:42:01,110
But you and I really hit it off.

716
00:42:01,110 --> 00:42:03,260
I knew it as soon as you walked in.

717
00:42:03,260 --> 00:42:05,336
You're a true savior of my family.

718
00:42:05,336 --> 00:42:07,620
- Me?
- When...

719
00:42:09,352 --> 00:42:11,667
I'm someone who likes to help others.

720
00:42:11,667 --> 00:42:14,748
But when did I save you?

721
00:42:14,748 --> 00:42:17,639
You were driving so slowly back then,

722
00:42:17,639 --> 00:42:19,312
causing me to miss my flight

723
00:42:19,312 --> 00:42:22,659
