724
00:42:22,659 --> 00:42:24,410
How could you have done that?

725
00:42:24,410 --> 00:42:26,150
- I... How...
- Hurry, say you're sorry.

726
00:42:26,150 --> 00:42:27,630
Sorry. My bad.

727
00:42:27,630 --> 00:42:28,610
Don't be.

728
00:42:28,610 --> 00:42:33,030
Thanks to missing that flight, I dodged
an investment trap.

729
00:42:33,030 --> 00:42:34,520
Really?

730
00:42:34,520 --> 00:42:36,090
That's some fate right there.

731
00:42:36,090 --> 00:42:38,610
And you're Xue Jiao's Dad.

732
00:42:38,610 --> 00:42:40,320
Are we destined or what?

733
00:42:40,320 --> 00:42:43,320
- Wait, this is...
- Don't drink too much.

734
00:42:43,320 --> 00:42:45,300
- Okay.
- She's right.

735
00:42:45,300 --> 00:42:47,360
You drink less, and I drink up.

736
00:42:47,360 --> 00:42:49,270
That way, our bond keeps going.

737
00:42:49,270 --> 00:42:52,070
- Right?
- Keep going.

738
00:42:52,070 --> 00:42:54,152
Good. Dad, Mom.

739
00:42:54,152 --> 00:42:57,950
Lin asked when we'd be available
to have another meal together.

740
00:42:57,950 --> 00:43:00,010
Another meal?

